Package: miniextendr
Title: Rust-R Interoperability Framework
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    c(
        person("Mossa M.", "Reimert", , "mossa@sund.ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("A2-AI", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
    )
Description: Provides a framework for building R packages with Rust backends.
    Enables seamless interoperability between R and Rust through procedural
    macros, automatic type conversion, external pointers with GC protection,
    ALTREP support, and safe multi-threading via worker threads.
